{"id": 2294, "genre": 1001, "title": "哪些“玩笑”你并不想开得起？", "description": "有些恶意满满的玩笑换个名字其实叫霸凌、骚扰、在违法边缘试探。（题图来自：iStock ©️ CSA-Printstock）", "record_count": 4032, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180423113717qj9eKPiJRIgQX7fb.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-05-02T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 279041, "content": "你的名字好难听啊，你年龄好大啊，你脸上好多痘痘啊，诶，开个玩笑你怎么还当真了！你脾气好差啊，跟你这种人玩真没意思。", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1332951}, {"id": 279297, "content": "打着哈哈随便用我的东西，明明跟你不是很熟", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1301968}, {"id": 279042, "content": "你真的好蠢哦，有时别人会这样开玩笑，但是这样会让人感觉很不自在", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1331015}, {"id": 279043, "content": "不要用玩笑的的语气说傻，逼，要说就认真肯定的说出这句话。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1106113}, {"id": 279044, "content": "你这么胖，不难过吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1330725}, {"id": 280837, "content": "玩笑这东西，目的是为了让讲笑话者自己开心而不是为了逗你开心。所以别人和你开玩笑，并不在乎你觉得好不好笑，说出来之后他们自己很开心，这就是他们唯一在乎的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1339411}, {"id": 279046, "content": "生病被人冷嘲热讽，她说她在开玩笑？！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1333073}, {"id": 280582, "content": "有些人总拿些低级趣味开涮，你不高兴了，反而认为你EQ特低。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 895190}, {"id": 279050, "content": "开玩笑地抢走我的东西，并且不还了。玛德我会记恨他一辈子。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 964934}, {"id": 279053, "content": "涉及到隐私和自尊问题的玩笑请不要随便开", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1333164}, {"id": 279054, "content": "猪跟你是一家人吧哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1298577}, {"id": 279056, "content": "关于我的初恋", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1328478}, {"id": 279057, "content": "有关亲人的！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1333198}, {"id": 279058, "content": "当众问：你是gay吗？那么……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1286903}, {"id": 279060, "content": "把低俗当幽默的老油条", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1282958}, {"id": 280596, "content": "把别人的自尊当玩笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1338367}, {"id": 296724, "content": "‘‘我是你爸爸’’‘‘你是我孙子’’‘‘你是不是喜欢某某’’你一句开玩笑就过去了？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1425655}, {"id": 279320, "content": "自以为十分风趣，实则无聊至极", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1308041}, {"id": 280090, "content": "真的很讨厌被说你好丑，好矮", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1334530}, {"id": 279837, "content": "任何说的过分的话，总以一句我是开玩笑的揭过，怕是情商太低吧。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1304404}, {"id": 279071, "content": "以好朋友的身份随便认识一个人就说我的黑料，说完我还不能不高兴，不然就是小气玩不起", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1120610}, {"id": 283683, "content": "经常说我gay，就算我是，你就不懂得一点点成年人社交礼仪吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1136135}, {"id": 279078, "content": "身体缺陷，很讨厌被人开玩笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1333327}, {"id": 281128, "content": "自嘲被当笑话，结果人家每天不停的讲", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1340321}, {"id": 279593, "content": "闹伴娘、不熟人士突然的黄色玩笑、莫名问工资", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1331215}, {"id": 279341, "content": "侮辱外形穿着", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1324911}, {"id": 280367, "content": "说你的缺点，虽然自己平时觉得没什么，但在和一群人聊天的时候，总会有朋友提起，虽知是玩笑，但是心里也会不开心。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1235774}, {"id": 279347, "content": "她想骂就骂，她说和好就和好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1334210}, {"id": 281912, "content": "有些事我自己可以自嘲，但我并不希望被别人嘲笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1345390}, {"id": 281402, "content": "168的和160的天天diss我158的矮", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1341150}, {"id": 280123, "content": "我开个玩笑而已，你这么认真干嘛？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1289003}, {"id": 281915, "content": "开第二次的玩笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1345391}, {"id": 280636, "content": "在东北某大，几个同学知道我听摇滚后:\n\"今天摇没摇啊？\"\n\"你这头发还是不够长啊\"\n\"去摇滚去吗？\"", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1338486}, {"id": 284734, "content": "讨厌别人碰我，无意识反应就很大。并不是在开玩笑啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1359987}, {"id": 279874, "content": "人身攻击", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 897572}, {"id": 281923, "content": "知道你哪里痛 打着开玩笑的名义来伤害你 对 这个人是我前男友", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1345422}, {"id": 277316, "content": "饭局上被人灌酒不能严肃拒绝，否则就是玩不起", "image": null, "praise_count": 847, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 280132, "content": "被室友泼脏水还要装作不在意", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1336082}, {"id": 277318, "content": "被后座同学抽掉凳子摔在地上，生气就是“闹着玩你咋还当真了”", "image": null, "praise_count": 132, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 280134, "content": "以自己的立场去解读你热爱的东西 对你热爱的东西不以为然还口口声声说是你不现实 生气后还问你至于吗不就是开个玩笑??", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1336078}, {"id": 281670, "content": "男生对女生开一些黄色玩笑，如果你生气又说你开不起玩笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1344316}, {"id": 277319, "content": "被起侮辱性的外号还要笑嘻嘻接受", "image": null, "praise_count": 520, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 279113, "content": "披着开玩笑的外套恶意嘲讽嫉妒的语句真的以为隐藏了吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 469911}, {"id": 277322, "content": "工作中被异性上司/客户说“没想到你身材还挺丰满/结实啊，多穿点这种凸显线条的衣服呗”", "image": null, "praise_count": 257, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 281424, "content": "不告诉而拍我照片录我视频并外传。教一个学生时发现她妈朋友圈一堆教室窗外偷拍孩子及老师同学的视频，我想骂人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1338331}, {"id": 295510, "content": "用侮辱性的语句说别人，别人一反驳，就是“玩不起”。不好意思，就是玩不起。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1414110}, {"id": 280153, "content": "先一嘴毒舌然后跟你说开玩笑的不要当真", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1253787}, {"id": 280413, "content": "第一次面基就\"啊，你的鹅蛋脸不见了…你皮肤不好，你说家乡话不好听\"…表现的不高兴了就说我跟我朋友都是互损的，我习惯了，你不要介意…\"你是在说我开不起玩笑吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1337701}, {"id": 280158, "content": "关于单身的玩笑。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1327630}, {"id": 278886, "content": "“我刚刚在开玩笑呢”本身就是一个开不起的玩笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 382, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1122099}]}